quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,"Alif Laam Miim."
  2,2,"Icyo ni igitabo (Qur’an) kidashidikanywaho, kikaba n’umuyoboro ku batinyamana."
  2,3,"Ba bandi bemera ibitagaragara (byahanuwe), bagahozaho iswala   (z’itegeko) kandi bagatanga mu byo twabahaye.",footnotes:1:Iswala ni inyito ya Kisilamu isobanura ibikorwa runaka biherekejwe n’imvugo runaka bitangirirwa n’ijambo Allah Akbar (Imana isumba byose), bigasozwa n’ijambo Assalaam Alaykum (amahoro y’Imana ababeho) ari byo twakwita Isengesho. Iswala ikaba irimo amoko abiri: Hari iz’itegeko ari zo Umuyisilamu ategetswe gukora ku munsi, n’izitari iz’itegeko z’umugereka twita (Sunat) zisobanurwa mu bitabo by’amategeko y’idini rya Isilamu (Fiq’hi).
  2,4,"Ni na bo bemera ibyo (wowe Muhamadi) wahishuriwe (Qur’an n’imigenzo y’Intumwa), bakanemera ibyahishuwe mbere yawe (ibitabo byahishuriwe Intumwa zakubanjirije), ndetse bakemera imperuka badashidikanya."
  2,5,"Abo ni bo bari mu nzira iboneye yagenwe na Nyagasani wabo, kandi ni bo bakiranutsi."